abstract: Two or three years since, the consumers of poetic literature were startled by the appearance of a timid little book called Passion Flowers. abstract: THE TRAGEDY AT MORAVIA-We have only a few particulars to add concerning the Moravia tragedy. The young woman, Miss SHAW, who was shot was alive as last evening, and some hopes are now entertained of her recovery.
